sources.title: Created Equal | Full Movie | Drama Thriller | Lou Diamond Phillips | Aaron Tveit
sources.description:
Created Equal - A cocky, up-and-coming attorney, begrudgingly takes on a case to sue the Archdiocese of New Orleans for sex discrimination; after a woman, who's desperate to become a priest, solicits his help.  
2017. Starring Lou Diamond Phillips, Aaron Tveit

metadata.Plot: An up-and-coming attorney takes on a case to sue the Catholic Church for discrimination against a young woman who desperately wants to become a priest. In a world where gender equality is a critical issue, the Church remains steeped in tradition. As the trial unfolds and divine authority is challenged, their lives become in danger as extremists plot to stop the heresy at any cost.
metadata.Writer: Ned Bowman, Michael Ricigliano Jr., Joyce Renee Lewis
metadata.Actors: Aaron Tveit, Edy Ganem, Lou Diamond Phillips
